Download and setup Windows Server 2022 as MAIN DC and Windows 10 as a CLIENT
Now, Windows Server 2022(MAIN DC)
Assign Ip add : 192.168.100.10 , Subnet mask : 255.255.255.0 , Default gate *Leaved blank* and DNS also same like IP address : 192.168.100.10 of MAIN DC
(DNS IMPORTANT)
Install Active Directory Domain Services, DNS, DHCP Server
After completed download Services
Add New forest domain in MAINDC to DOMAIN *manoj.com* ]- Company name i used as Manoj
Created users from Active Directory users and Computers
user1 - person1
user2 - helpdesk
user3 - admin
Added Windows 10 to domain - *manoj.com*
Setup Attacker as *Kali Linux* 
